@JanProvaznik  please let us know when labeler feels better :)
@YuliiaKovalova I disabled it since we don't use PR labels so on subsequent PRs it will not show up, it's not a required check so we can merge with no problems.

Is it intentional that the roslyn channel is still VS 17.14 while everyone else moved to the next version?

> https://github.com/dotnet/roslyn (VS 17.14) ==> 'https://github.com/dotnet/msbuild' ('main')

Asking as the use of the older compiler is causing issues in https://github.com/dotnet/dotnet/pull/227
